  "background": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464802688315-7fa6235125f6",
  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch1",
      "text": "The engines just cut out completely. Everything’s dead, Bob. What the hell happened?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch2",
      "text": "We hit some kind of dampening field. All power’s being drained faster than I can reroute it.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch3",
      "text": "Great. Any bright ideas before we become space popsicles?",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch4",
      "text": "I’m detecting an ancient structure ahead. It’s the source of the field… and the only thing with power for light-years.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch5",
      "text": "So we either drift forever or check out the creepy alien ruin that’s eating our energy. Fun choices.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch6",
      "text": "Suit thrusters still have thirty minutes of juice. We can reach it before total blackout.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch7",
      "text": "Then let’s move before I change my mind.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch8",
      "text": "EVA in three… two… one. Pushing off now.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch9",
      "text": "This thing is massive. Look at those glyphs—they’re glowing.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Alex", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/focalpoint.png" },
      "isUser": true
    },
    {
      "chapter_id": "ch10",
      "text": "And getting brighter the closer we get. Whatever’s inside knows we’re coming.",
      "content_image": null,
      "character": { "name": "Bob", "image": "https://ix-marketing.imgix.net/footer-image.png" },
      "isUser": false
    }
  ],
  "choices": [
    { "text": "Enter the ancient alien structure", "next_scene": "scene2" }
